.TH HYPRLAND\-DONATE\-SCREEN 1 "2025-11-20" "hyprland-guiutils 0.2.1" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprland\-donate\-screen \- display the Hyprland donation prompt
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprland\-donate\-screen
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprland\-donate\-screen
is a GUI utility that displays a screen prompting users to support
Hyprland development.
It provides a "Support" button that opens the Hyprland support page in
the default browser, and a "No thanks" button to dismiss.
.PP
This utility is invoked automatically by Hyprland and is not typically
run directly by users.
.PP
The window class is
.BR hyprland\-donate\-screen .
.SH OPTIONS
None.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1),
.BR hyprland\-welcome (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/hyprwm/hyprland-guiutils/issues
.UE .
